title: Carlyle Jr. Suite w. balcony, downtown/lake views
posting_body: ['Junior 1 Bedroom, suite on 14th floor.', 'Heat and Air Conditioning, Hot Water, Cooking gas included in Rent.', 'New laminate flooring.', 'Stove, refrigerator provided..', 'Small electric bill, about $15/mo.', 'Free WiFi in lobby and common areas.', 'Downtown/Lake views from LR, BR and balcony.', 'Unbelievable amenities including two pools (indoor/outdoor), jacuzzi, racquetball court, deli, new exercise room, sauna, etc.', 'No dishwasher.', 'See <URL> for more pictures.', 'This is a small unit and really only room for one person, NON-SMOKER.', ' One cat okay w extra Security Deposit.', 'Indoor garage space available for extra charge.', ' Available 10/1.', ' Land line 4 four o. 5seven9, 5eight2six.', 'LR 20\'6 x 10\'9"', 'Bedroom 13\'8" x 9\'4"', 'Bedroom Closet 4\'5" x 2\'4" deep', 'Foyer Closet  4\'5" x 2\' deep', 'Kitchen 5\' x 7\'3"', 'AMAZING views of downtown skyline, Edgewater Beach and Lake Erie.', ' There is also a balcony.', ' Available June 1.']
